messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacation Village Resorts. This is Jamie, a virtual agent on a recorded line. How can I help you today?
Questions regarding a bill.
Let me check on your billing details. Can you tell me which resort your bill is for?
Just to clarify, are you asking about your yearly maintenance bill or your mortgage bill?
Maintenance bill.
Alright, I can help with that. Can you give me the phone number you have on your
contract?
Two zero one two one three eight zero eight zero.
One moment please, let me check that for you.
I was able to pull up a matching record using your phone number. Can you tell me your first and last
name?
Vincent Creo.
I have a record on file, but the name I have does not match. Can you please
spell your first and last name for me?
Valerie Creo.
Thanks for clarifying. Can you tell me your state
of residence?
New Jersey.
You're verified. Go ahead and tell me what you need help
with regarding your maintenance bill.
Whose address is on file?
The address I have on file is forty-one Madison Avenue,
number eleven A, Madison, New Jersey, zero seven nine four zero. What would you like to do next regarding your maintenance bill?
Who owns the unit?
The owner on file for Vacation Village at Williamsburg, unit two one nine, contract number three eight one nine three four, is Valerie Creo.
What else would you like to know about this contract?
That's it for now.
Is there anything else I can help you with today?
No. That's it.
Alright, have a great day.
Goodbye.
